latestPosts.caption:
You don’t become a jury every other day so THIS WAS SPECIAL!🥹💕 And tons of thanks to @cholafashions cause they insisted i can look beautiful withiut compromising on my fractured leg! Use my referral code (mentioned at the end of the video) for additional discounts! 💸

Why was this special? Cause that moment when a parent walked upto me and said,”thank you so much for making my child comfortable on stage” 😩 built my self esteem too high! I myself didn’t know i could be so so good with kids and asking age appropriate questions, without making them feel overwhelmed! Thank you @ikfw_official for believing in me!
